            . I am journeyman to Mr. Ingram, a <rs id="t18320216-246-viclabel1398" type="occupation">coach-maker</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320216-246-victim2056 t18320216-246-viclabel1398"></join>, of <placeName id="t18320216-246-crimeloc1399">Great Queen-street, Lincoln's Inn-fields</placeName>
